{"data":[{"date":"19:21 13/07","title":"HLV Emery h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/hlv-emery-hua-hen-arsenal-se-co-them-bom-tan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 tham v\u1ecdng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c mua s\u1eafm</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 5 t\u00e2n binh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 bao g\u1ed3m Lucas Torreira, Bernd Leno, Sokratis Papastathopoulos, Matteo Guendouzi v\u00e0 Stephan Lichtsteiner. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng vi\u00ean g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng n\u00ean tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Unai Emery t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho nh\u1eefng Per Mertesacker, Jack Wilshere v\u00e0 Santi Cazorla \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Arsenal. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/HLV-Emery-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lucas Torreira l\u00e0 1 trong 5 t\u00e2n binh Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn kh\u00f4ng khi n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cH\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1ed5n. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c mua s\u1eafm khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1edf c\u1eeda v\u1edbi \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i mua b\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m. V\u00e0 Emery d\u00f9 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emery tro thanh HLV Arsenal\" title=\"Emery tro thanh HLV Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/Arsenal-chieu-mo-Torreira-Tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal v\u00e0 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n \"bom t\u1ea5n\"</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 khi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1ecd\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 46 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i. \u201cTh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u1eb7c ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 xem li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho Arsenal hay kh\u00f4ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Emery tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Boreham Wood cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi Singapore d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-hang-hot-ligue-1-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191053.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: H\u00e0ng hot Ligue 1 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-so-huu-tan-binh-thu-5-172-190980.html\">N\u00d3NG: Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 5</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-xac-nhan-co-tan-binh-thu-4-tri-gia-30-trieu-euro-172-190886.html\">Arsenal CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-arsenal-chi-35-trieu-euro-mua-andre-gomes-172-190877.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Andre Gomes?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wenger-bat-bai-khoi-arsenal-vikante-172-190866.html\">Wenger b\u1eadt b\u00e3i kh\u1ecfi Arsenal v\u00ec...Kante?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-bernd-leno-chinh-thuc-chon-so-ao-o-arsenal-172-190840.html\">T\u00e2n binh Bernd Leno ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1232","checkdouble":"191120"},{"date":"20:00 13/07","title":"M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus t\u00ednh t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/15/muon-oai-ronaldo-juventus-tinh-tai-hop-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba c\u1ee7a Man United. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t Miralem Pjanic v\u00e0o tay c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d hy v\u1ecdng uy danh c\u1ee7a si\u00eau t\u00e2n binh Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a Pogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ch\u1ed1n x\u01b0a.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pjanic b\u1ecb chi\u00eau d\u1ee5</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus t\u1eeb AS Roma \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2016/17, Miralem Pjanic \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia & Herzegovina \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed7i khi v\u1eafng \u0111i Pjanic, Juventus l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c lao \u0111ao \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Bianconeri hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba c\u1ee7a Man United h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba c\u1ee7a Man United h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/24/Muon-oai-Ronaldo,-Juventus-muon-mua-Pogba-cua-Man-United-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pjanic \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0 Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c Pjanic c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Barcelona hay Man City. Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 5 s\u1ebd m\u1ed9t l\u00f2ng, m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1 v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juve t\u00ednh t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t, Juventus thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Pjanic \u1edf l\u1ea1i. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, h\u1ecd t\u00ednh s\u1eb5n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B n\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n x\u1ea3y ra. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Pjanic \u1edf khu trung tuy\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Paul Pogba\" title=\"tien ve Paul Pogba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/messi-muon-barca-mua-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-lich-su-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba c\u1ee7a Man United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016, Juve \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Pjanic v\u1ec1 thay Pogba gia nh\u1eadp M.U v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u chuy\u1ebfn quay l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u1ee7a Pogba t\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay kh\u00f4ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh. Anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 v\u00e0 b\u1ecb t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn Anh t\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Pjanic \u0111i theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a Barca hay Man City, Juventus d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a Pogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin m\u1edbi chi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus hy v\u1ecdng tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng Ronaldo s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Pogba m\u1ee7i l\u00f2ng. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Pjanic (n\u1ebfu anh ra \u0111i) c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Allianz sau 2 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/luka-modric-noi-gi-khi-ronaldo-toi-juventus-180-191085.html\">Luka Modric n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\">M.U \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201csao b\u1ef1\u201d Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-phai-toi-juventus-vi-messi-184-191064.html\">Ronaldo ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi Juventus v\u00ec\u2026 Messi?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do-421-191051.html\">Ronaldo sang Juve: Qu\u00e2n domino tr\u00ean TTCN \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1231","checkdouble":"191121"},{"date":"20:37 13/07","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean r\u1eddi Leicester","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/muc-tieu-cua-mu-duoc-khuyen-roi-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Colombia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Camp Nou.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb sau World Cup</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina gia nh\u1eadp Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 11,8 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1edbi nay, trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i La Liga khi HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u01b0a th\u00edch nh\u1eefng Gerard Pique, Samuel Umtiti r\u1ed3i c\u1ea3 Thomas Vermaelen h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau World Cup 2018, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Mina \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Anh ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 sau 4 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Colombia v\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean, anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00f9 \u1edf Barcelona hay \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB kh\u00e1c trong m\u00f9a 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Yerry-Mina-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mina t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Colombia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u00edt \u00e1p l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n v\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean&rdquo;, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia n\u00f3i. &ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, v\u00ec CLB c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t huy \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 n\u01a1i n\u00e0o d\u00f9 \u1edf Barcelona hay ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u00c1p l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMina k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi gian \u1edf Barcelona m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb HLV Valverde g\u1ea1t kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n. &ldquo;C\u00f3 l\u00fac t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc trong c\u00e1c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn&rdquo;, anh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina cua Barca\" title=\"Yerry Mina cua Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Yerry-Mina-cua-Barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh \u1edf nh\u00e0. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi xem c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qua TV, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i bu\u1ed3n b\u1ef1c v\u00ec th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n t\u1ea1i Barcelona.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 tin Everton \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi Mina. H\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu trung v\u1ec7 cao t\u1edbi 1m94.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-sao-khung-chelsea-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-191104.html\">Barca chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Chelsea n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-nang-gia-hoi-mua-willian-cua-chelsea-180-191078.html\">Barca n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-mua-hazard-cua-chelsea-180-191016.html\">Barca l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u1eabng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-sap-co-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018-180-190985.html\">H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Barca trong h\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-cu-nguoi-den-phap-dam-phan-mua-rabiot-180-190971.html\">Barca c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua sao PSG</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1230","checkdouble":"191122"},{"date":"21:18 13/07","title":"River Plate b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 sao m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 Tottenham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/river-plate-bao-gia-sao-moi-noi-cho-real-madrid-va-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>River Plate ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Quintero v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro. CLB Argentina c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i sao m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Tottenham.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Quintero n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u1edd World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGia nh\u1eadp River Plate d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Porto t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Juan Fernando Quintero. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea1i g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Argentina, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1ecf con n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i th\u00edch nghi nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQuintero \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0110T Colombia tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, anh ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Los Cafeteros sau 4 tr\u1eadn. D\u00f9 Colombia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i xa nh\u01b0ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn lan t\u1ecfa sang ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"River Plate ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Quintero v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"River Plate ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Quintero v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/River-Plate-chi-ban-Quintero-voi-gia-25-trieu-Euro-cho-Real-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Quintero ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Anh l\u00e0 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Tottenham c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a Quintero v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng c\u00f3 19 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Colombia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>River Plate b\u00e1o gi\u00e1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd v\u1edbi Porto, River Plate c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t Quintero v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2019. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 sau World Cup r\u1eb1ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u00e1t khao ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho c\u00e1c CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng quy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda River. V\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, Rodolfo D'Onofrio th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang n\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 c\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"quintero River Plate\" title=\"quintero River Plate\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/quintero-River-Plate.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>River Plate ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Quintero v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho Quintero. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i River. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Quintero ra \u0111i, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i b\u1eb1ng l\u00f2ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, D'Onofrio kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Quintero. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u River so s\u00e1nh anh v\u1edbi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina, Juan Roman Riquelme. \u201cQuintero khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i nh\u1edb t\u1edbi Riquelme\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u00f3c quan s\u00e1t t\u1ed1t. Quintero c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn sang b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra b\u00ean tr\u00e1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1229","checkdouble":"191123"},{"date":"22:02 13/07","title":"Griezmann: \u201c\u0110\u1eebng gh\u00e9p t\u00ean t\u00f4i v\u1edbi Zidane\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/griezmann-dung-ghep-ten-toi-voi-zidane.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Antoine Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch th\u00fa khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t cho bi\u1ec7t danh \u201cGrizou\u201d nh\u1eb1m so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Zinedine Zidane.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch bi\u1ec7t danh Grizou</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAntoine Griezmann l\u00ean 7 tu\u1ed5i khi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup 1998, n\u01a1i Zinedine Zidane l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap \u1edf chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Brazil. 20 n\u0103m sau, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong m\u0169i \u0111inh ba c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Olivier Giroud v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe, Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 3 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u1eb7t cho bi\u1ec7t danh \u201cGrizou\u201d, l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb c\u00e1i t\u00ean Zizou c\u1ee7a Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antoine Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0110\u1eebng gh\u00e9p t\u00ean t\u00f4i v\u1edbi Zidane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Antoine Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0110\u1eebng gh\u00e9p t\u00ean t\u00f4i v\u1edbi Zidane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Antoine-Griezmann-phat-bieu-Dung-ghep-ten-toi-voi-Zidane-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Griezmann c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbp Antoine Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecb gh\u00e9p t\u00ean v\u1edbi Zidane. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 th\u00edch c\u00e1i t\u00ean Grizou\u201d, anh n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 t\u00f4i nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7. T\u00f4i th\u00edch ch\u01a1i game Fortnite c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y, t\u00f4i th\u00edch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, t\u00f4i th\u00edch u\u1ed1ng tr\u00e0 mate. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Griezmann kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p khi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Craotia c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Les Bleus m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n sau 6 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi 3 trong \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Argentina.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann cua Phap\" title=\"Griezmann cua Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Griezmann-cua-Phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Antoine Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Ho\u1eb7c v\u1edbi Mbappe \u1edf b\u00ean c\u00e1nh, ho\u1eb7c Giroud \u1edf trung t\u00e2m ho\u1eb7c v\u1edbi t\u00f4i trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra nh\u01b0 \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, Griezmann c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup (Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng). \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng\u201d, anh n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m c\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng hay kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/croatia-truoc-tran-gap-phap-tinh-than-co-khoa-lap-yeu-to-the-luc-421-191115.html\">Croatia tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p: Tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00f3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-diem-mat-3-cap-doi-dau-dang-cho-doi-421-191119.html\">Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1eb7t 3 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-phap-se-vo-dich-421-191099.html\">Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: 4 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-qua-thua-loi-the-so-voi-croatia-mourinho-che-trach-btc-world-cup-421-191082.html\">Ph\u00e1p qu\u00e1 th\u1eeba l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf so v\u1edbi Croatia, Mourinho ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch BTC World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-vao-chung-ket-gap-phap-dt-anh-bi-mbappe-cuoi-vao-mat-421-191017.html\">\u0110\u00f2i v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p, \u0110T Anh b\u1ecb Mbappe c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1228","checkdouble":"191124"},{"date":"22:28 13/07","title":"Sao s\u00e1ng World Cup th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u201c\u0111\u00e1\u201d kh\u1ecfi Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/sao-sang-world-cup-thua-nhan-co-the-bi-da-khoi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Colombia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Camp Nou.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb sau World Cup</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina gia nh\u1eadp Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 11,8 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1edbi nay, trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i La Liga khi HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u01b0a th\u00edch nh\u1eefng Gerard Pique, Samuel Umtiti r\u1ed3i c\u1ea3 Thomas Vermaelen h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau World Cup 2018, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Mina \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Anh ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 sau 4 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Colombia v\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean, anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00f9 \u1edf Barcelona hay \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB kh\u00e1c trong m\u00f9a 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Yerry-Mina-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mina t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Colombia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u00edt \u00e1p l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n v\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean&rdquo;, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia n\u00f3i. &ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, v\u00ec CLB c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t huy \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 n\u01a1i n\u00e0o d\u00f9 \u1edf Barcelona hay ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u00c1p l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMina k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi gian \u1edf Barcelona m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb HLV Valverde g\u1ea1t kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n. &ldquo;C\u00f3 l\u00fac t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc trong c\u00e1c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn&rdquo;, anh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina cua Barca\" title=\"Yerry Mina cua Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Yerry-Mina-cua-Barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh \u1edf nh\u00e0. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi xem c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qua TV, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i bu\u1ed3n b\u1ef1c v\u00ec th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n t\u1ea1i Barcelona.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 tin Everton \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi Mina. H\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu trung v\u1ec7 cao t\u1edbi 1m94.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-sao-khung-chelsea-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-191104.html\">Barca chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Chelsea n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-nang-gia-hoi-mua-willian-cua-chelsea-180-191078.html\">Barca n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-mua-hazard-cua-chelsea-180-191016.html\">Barca l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u1eabng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-sap-co-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018-180-190985.html\">H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Barca trong h\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-cu-nguoi-den-phap-dam-phan-mua-rabiot-180-190971.html\">Barca c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua sao PSG</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1227","checkdouble":"191127"},{"date":"23:19 13/07","title":"Liverpool t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u: Tam t\u1ea5u k\u1ebb \u1edf, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/liverpool-toi-my-du-dau-tam-tau-ke-o-nguoi-di.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Sadio Mane sau khi d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu Roberto Firmino v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Salah v\u00e0 Mane tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Sadio Mane s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm k\u1ebft th\u00fac chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Senegal. \u0110\u1ebfn nay, Salah v\u00e0 Mane \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y khi The Kop sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Salah b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp v\u1edbi Uruguay do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng vai v\u00e0 h\u1ecd thua 0-1. 2 tr\u1eadn sau, m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u ghi b\u00e0n song \u201cC\u00e1c Pharaoh\u201d v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Salah-va-Mane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Salah v\u00e0 Mane c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Mane, Senegal c\u1ee7a Anh th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan. Sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 thi\u1ebfu Firmino</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i M\u1ef9, Liverpool s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup v\u1edbi Dortmund, Man City v\u00e0 Man United. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e1 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Napoli v\u00e0 Torino v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roberto Firmino chan thuong\" title=\"Roberto Firmino ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/neville-khuyen-mu-chieu-mo-sao-khung-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Firmino v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean v\u00e0o s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 th\u00eam</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn khi \u0111\u00f3, Liverpool m\u1edbi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Roberto Firmino. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f9ng \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9. Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 bao g\u1ed3m Jordan Henderson v\u00e0 Trent Alexander-Arnold (Anh), Simon Mignolet (B\u1ec9) v\u00e0 Dejan Lovren (Croatia). H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 7 ng\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League v\u1edbi West Ham v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 12/8.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-thua-nuoc-duc-tha-cau-vu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-172-191026.html\">Liverpool th\u1eeba n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ee5c th\u1ea3 c\u00e2u v\u1ee5 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-mung-ro-voi-man-trinh-dien-cua-2-tan-binh-bom-tan-172-190681.html\">Klopp m\u1eebng r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a 2 t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam-172-190673.html\">Sadio Mane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish-172-190672.html\">Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u0103n sao tr\u1ebb h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-khong-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-fekir-172-190670.html\">Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Fekir</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1226","checkdouble":"191136"},{"date":"05:58 14/07","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 Xherdan Shaqiri sau khi k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Stoke City.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mua Shaqiri t\u1eeb Stoke v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chuy\u1ec7n Xherdan Shaqiri ra \u0111i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y v\u1ed1n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra, sau khi Stoke City c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng khi ngay sau World Cup 2018 chinh chi\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Champions League d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mua Shaqiri t\u1eeb Stoke v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n s\u1ed1 \u00e1o 23 quen thu\u1ed9c \u1edf s\u00e2n Anfield, Shaqiri h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \u201cL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, anh lu\u00f4n mong mu\u1ed1n m\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t, nh\u1eefng s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb v\u00e0i n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh. D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e2u v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac.\u201d \u2013 T\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 g\u1ee3i nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i n\u0103m 2014 khi Bayern Munich kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n anh cho Liverpool, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i sai l\u1ea7m sang Inter Milan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i, s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t HLV tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 g\u00f3p s\u1ee9c cho Liverpool gi\u00e0nh m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u danh gi\u00e1 trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Chinh-thuc-Liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-Xherdan-Shaqiri-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mua Shaqiri t\u1eeb Stoke v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Shaqiri tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb CLB qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Basel tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t gia nh\u1eadp Bayern Munich c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Inter Milan v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2012 v\u00e0 2015. Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh ph\u1ea3i lang b\u1ea1t sang Anh gia nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t Stoke khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i tr\u1ea3i qua ba m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i h\u1ed3i sinh s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Xherdan Shaqiri tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 ba gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 sau hai qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ea3 tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u1eb1m gia c\u1ed1 khu v\u1ef1c trung tuy\u1ebfn - Naby Keita t\u1eeb RB Leipzig v\u00e0 Fabinho t\u1eeb Monaco.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/xherdan-shaqiri-va-tinh-yeu-voi-hai-mau-co-389-190288.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/xherdan-shaqiri-va-tinh-yeu-voi-hai-mau-co.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/xherdan-shaqiri-va-tinh-yeu-voi-hai-mau-co-389-190288.html\">Xherdan Shaqiri v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u1edbi hai m\u00e0u c\u1edd</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o t\u00f4i c\u00f2n 16 tu\u1ed5i, c\u1eaft c\u1ecf trong v\u01b0\u1eddn c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 n\u0103m 18 tu\u1ed5i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ean chuy\u1ebfn bay t\u1edbi Nam Phi d\u1ef1 World Cup.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1225","checkdouble":"191137"},{"date":"06:24 14/07","title":"Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Neymar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-ra-thong-bao-ve-thuong-vu-neymar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trang ch\u1ee7 CLB ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng b\u00e0i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao Neymar t\u1eeb Paris Saint-Germain.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar t\u1eeb PSG?</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar s\u1edbm b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi ch\u1ec9 sau v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 222 tri\u1ec7u Euro sang Paris Saint-Germain. \u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00f4ng cao c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p hay nh\u1eefng v\u1ee5 l\u00f9m x\u00f9m m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, ng\u00f4i sao Brazil ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i ngay \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng, khi Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o c\u0169 Barcelona m\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-neu-neymar-toi-real-madrid-va-su-run-ray-cua-messilona-180-186568.html\" target=\"_blank\">gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid</span>, kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1n b\u00e3o t\u1ed1 th\u1ecbnh n\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Cules.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng mua Neymar t\u1eeb PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng mua Neymar t\u1eeb PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-ra-thong-bao-ve-thuong-vu-neymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng mua Neymar t\u1eeb PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 Kh\u00f4ng!</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ch\u00ednh nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Champions League m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb thu\u1edf nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e2ng cao v\u1ecb th\u1ebf v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, danh ti\u1ebfng thay th\u1ebf ch\u00ednh Cristiano Ronaldo, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Bernabeu sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady gi\u1eefa mu\u00f4n tr\u00f9ng v\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, Real Madrid m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Neymar ngay tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 CLB. N\u1ed9i dung b\u00e1c b\u1ecf \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao Brazil c\u1ee7a Los Blancos c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Neymar, Real Madrid xin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn Paris Saint-Germain c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Real v\u00e0 PSG c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p n\u00ean n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh giao d\u1ecbch mua b\u00e1n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Neymar kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi PSG m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trong khi Real Madrid c\u00f3 l\u1ebd d\u1ea7n chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau bom t\u1ea5n kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang l\u00e0 Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u1edbi c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-neu-neymar-toi-real-madrid-va-su-run-ray-cua-messilona-180-186568.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/goc-nhin-neu-neymar-toi-real-madrid-va-su-run-ray-cua-messilona.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-neu-neymar-toi-real-madrid-va-su-run-ray-cua-messilona-180-186568.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Neymar t\u1edbi Real v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 run r\u1ea9y c\u1ee7a \u201cMessilona\u201d</span><br>\r\nTheo Lionel Messi, vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh n\u1ebfu Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp v\u1edbi Barcelona. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thien-ac-noi-neymar-ca-nhan-da-bao-gio-lon-hon-tap-the-421-190529.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/thien-ac-noi-neymar-ca-nhan-da-bao-gio-lon-hon-tap-the.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thien-ac-noi-neymar-ca-nhan-da-bao-gio-lon-hon-tap-the-421-190529.html\">Thi\u1ec7n \u00e1c n\u01a1i Neymar: C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 bao gi\u1edd l\u1edbn h\u01a1n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3?</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u0103n th\u01a1 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 s\u1ebfn s\u00faa, ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o l\u1ed7i th\u1eddi n\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ch\u1ea5t thanh cao truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng anh h\u00f9ng trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y nay. Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1224","checkdouble":"191138"},{"date":"06:51 14/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Anh (21h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7): M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00ec m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/14/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-anh-21h00-ngay-147-moi-nguoi-vi-mot-nguoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a nh\u01b0 tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup, c\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Anh c\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong th\u1ebf ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u, tr\u00ean h\u1ebft v\u00ec cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh Chi\u1ebfc Gi\u00e0y V\u00e0ng gi\u1eefa hai ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c con c\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\u2026 t\u1ed1n th\u1eddi gian</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Euro kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3, Copa America kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3, Asian Cup kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3, CAN kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed AFF Cup c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng b\u00e3i b\u1ecf t\u1eeb l\u00e2u, tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb khai t\u1eed trong c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, t\u1eeb ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn\u2026 ao l\u00e0ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Olympics l\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7 b\u1edfi s\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh t\u00edch to\u00e0n \u0111o\u00e0n, trong khi ngay \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i danh gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 World Cup, tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba v\u1eabn c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng su\u1ed1t 88 n\u0103m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 b\u1ee7a v\u00e2y xung quanh b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Anh 21h00 ng\u00e0y 147 tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Anh 21h00 ng\u00e0y 147 tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/333.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018: Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a!</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u0111i n\u00f3i l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 10 n\u0103m nay r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd n\u00ean di\u1ec5n ra. Th\u1ee9 mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a duy nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup l\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 t\u1ed5\u2026 t\u1ed1n th\u1eddi gian.\u201d \u2013 Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Louis Van Gaal sau khi \u00f4ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil trong\u2026 tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2014.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0\u2026 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a, t\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 \u00e9p bu\u1ed9c hai k\u1ebb chi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1i g\u1eafng g\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau n\u1ed7i \u0111au \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, trong khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t m\u00e0 tranh th\u1ee7 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n d\u1ea7n h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n l\u00ean CLB \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ebb th\u1eafng th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eb7n ngo\u00e0i ch\u00fat \u00edt an \u1ee7i v\u00e0 t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00f4 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb, trong khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua ch\u1ec9 c\u00e0ng th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ed1n \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb9p trong m\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. C\u00e1i h\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh y\u1ebfu khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1eef d\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-bi-tinh-nhuong-nhau-thang-dung-bien-minh-thanh-con-tin-cua-su-may-rui-421-189869.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/anh-bi-tinh-nhuong-nhau-thang-dung-bien-minh-thanh-con-tin-cua-su-may-rui.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-bi-tinh-nhuong-nhau-thang-dung-bien-minh-thanh-con-tin-cua-su-may-rui-421-189869.html\">Anh \u2013 B\u1ec9 t\u00ednh\u2026 nh\u01b0\u1eddng nhau th\u1eafng? \u0110\u1eebng bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh con tin c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 may r\u1ee7i!</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9m h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn \u0111i tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G s\u1ebd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u knock-out d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u01a1n \u1edf World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00ec th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n danh d\u1ef1,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn\u2026 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ec9 vs Anh tho\u1ea1t nghe kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u00f3ng tr\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1eb1ng n\u00e0y t\u1eadn hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u1edf World Cup 2018 th\u00ec c\u00f2n g\u00ec b\u1eb1ng. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a di\u1ec5n ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc 21h00 t\u1ed1i nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Anh (21h00 ng\u00e0y 147) M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00ec m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Anh (21h00 ng\u00e0y 147) M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00ec m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/Nhan-dinh-Bi-vs-Anh-(21h00-ngay-147)-Moi-nguoi-vi-mot-nguoi-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018: M\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 sau hai tu\u1ea7n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a x\u00e9t tr\u00ean t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang. \u1ede v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1edbm ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 h\u00ecnh trung tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1eb3ng ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec, khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c nh\u1eb1m tr\u00e1nh nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u knock-out ch\u00f4ng gai h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho B\u1ec9 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn d\u00e0n sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean y\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh thua \u201cc\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea5y\u201d nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i c\u00f3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 B\u1ec9, \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft m\u00e0 l\u00e0 tranh h\u1ea1ng ba. H\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf v\u00e0 Tam S\u01b0 ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i nh\u00ecn Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Croatia d\u1eaft tay nhau tranh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du am Anh vs Croatia\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/nguoi-anh-ha-quyet-tam-gianh-huy-chuong-dong-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018: Hai b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i nh\u00ecn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia tranh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba n\u00e0y, B\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Anh, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00ean kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c. Chuy\u1ec7n Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, gi\u00e0 d\u01a1 h\u01a1n Anh \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, x\u00e9t tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh hay \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p ng\u00f4i sao v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng sau c\u00fa v\u1ea5p ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1eeda thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Anh \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn h\u01a1n khi b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t Croatia c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, trong khi vi\u1ec7c B\u1ec9 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n d\u00f9 sao c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m khi nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi 30, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 n\u00ean c\u00f3 c\u00e1i k\u1ebft \u0111\u1eb9p b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0110TQG.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-anh-vs-croatia-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-191004.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/DT-Anh-that-bai-vi-thieu-mot-cau-thu-sang-tao-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-anh-vs-croatia-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-191004.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh g\u00e1c l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng: B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, v\u1eady th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 sao?</span><br>\r\nB\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ed3i. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y sau khi ti\u1ec5n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi y\u00ean v\u1ecb \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">90 ph\u00fat cho ri\u00eang hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t n\u00f3i v\u1eady c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd thi\u1ebfu c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb trung n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai x\u00e1n l\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft. Tam S\u01b0 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u1eafng thua th\u00ec c\u0169ng v\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n v\u00ec m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f2n ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua Ph\u00e1 L\u01b0\u1edbi v\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn so v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Romelu Lukaku b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tranh Chi\u1ebfc Gi\u00e0y V\u00e0ng World Cup 2018. Trung phong c\u1ee7a Man Utd t\u1edbi gi\u1edd m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Anh (21h00 ng\u00e0y 147) M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00ec m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Anh (21h00 ng\u00e0y 147) M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00ec m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/nguoi-anh-phan-doi-y-do-nhuong-nhin-bi-vi-dai-cuc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018: H\u1ed3i k\u1ebft cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng Kane vs Lukaku</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u00f3i \u0111i n\u00f3i l\u1ea1i, c\u1ea3 Kane v\u00e0 Lukaku c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng qua \u0111\u00f3 sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n knock-out t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i y\u00ean h\u01a1i l\u1eb7ng ti\u1ebfng. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, 90% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m h\u1ebft \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u00e0 v\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng, c\u1ea3 hai HLV Gareth Southgate v\u00e0 Roberto Martinez c\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1eabn s\u1ebd tung ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh tr\u00ean c\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 cho tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a n\u00e0y, v\u1eeba h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i m\u00ecnh n\u1ed5 s\u00fang v\u1eeba ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u00f3i v\u1eady th\u00f4i ch\u1ee9 v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Lukaku c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eadt k\u00e8o, danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc Gi\u00e0y V\u00e0ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Kane, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 t\u00ednh thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 cao (5/6 b\u00e0n \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama, 3 penalty v\u00e0 1 \u0111\u1eadp ch\u00e2n may m\u1eafn). <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Quan tr\u1ecdng g\u00ec, ng\u00f4i sao Tottenham v\u1eabn t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng ni\u1ec1m vui tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Vua Ph\u00e1 L\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sau ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i Gary Lineker \u1edf Mexico 1986.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-o-tran-colombia-vs-anh-nguoi-thu-linh-phot-tinh-ang-le-421-190324.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/du-am-colombia-vs-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-o-tran-colombia-vs-anh-nguoi-thu-linh-phot-tinh-ang-le-421-190324.html\">Harry Kane: G\u00e3 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh \u201cph\u1edbt t\u1ec9nh \u0102ng-l\u00ea\u201d</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford v\u1eabn x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n vinh nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u00eam l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sang trang cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, nh\u01b0ng sao ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Anh:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ec9 (3-4-3): 1. Courtois; 2. Alderweireld \u2013 4. Kompany \u2013 5. Vertonghen; 15. Meunier \u2013 6. Witsel \u2013 8. Fellaini \u2013 22. Chadli; 7. De Bruyne \u2013 9. Lukaku \u2013 10. Hazard<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh (3-5-2): 1. Pickford; 2. Walker \u2013 5. Stones \u2013 6. Maguire; 22. Alexander-Arnold \u2013 7. Lingard \u2013 4. Dier \u2013 17. Delph \u2013 3. Rose; 9. Kane \u2013 11. Vardy<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Anh: 2-1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1223","checkdouble":"191141"},{"date":"14:52 13/07","title":"Barca chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Chelsea n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/15/barca-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-sao-khung-chelsea-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Blues nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kante</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, vi\u1ec7c Iniesta sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Paulinho tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c khi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd m\u1ecfng \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. HLV Ernesto Valverde \u01b0u ti\u00ean vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve NGolo Kante\" title=\"tien ve NGolo Kante\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/6/thuc-hu-vu-psg-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-kante.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua NGolo Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n The Blues chi \u0111\u1eadm cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, anh duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Kante s\u1edf h\u1eefu n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111eo b\u00e1m d\u1ebbo dai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Barca s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Barca c\u00f3 Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n Kante, Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, The Blues ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb Leicester.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Barca-muon-mua-Kante-cua-Chelsea-voi-gia-60-trieu-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Barca c\u00f3 Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea s\u1ebd l\u00e3i l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Kante cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha. HLV Maurizio Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea thay Conte mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 The Blues gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1eeb Chelsea, Barca c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Mirror cho r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-psg-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-kante-172-190952.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kante</span>, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng Andre Gomes \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Blues nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1222","checkdouble":"191104"},{"date":"15:18 13/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Man City b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c Sterling tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e3o ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/de-bruyne-phat-bieu-ve-sterling-dong-doi-tai-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kevin De Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sterling, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Man City. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e0n em kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn sau World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sterling m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee9 7 n\u00e0y, khi B\u1ec9 g\u1eb7p Anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fac m\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 th\u00fa v\u1ecb gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Man City l\u00e0 Kevin De Bruyne v\u00e0 Raheem Sterling di\u1ec5n ra. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 De Bruyne t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh th\u00ec Sterling l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1. Su\u1ed1t 5 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n sau 6 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i World Cup, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u l\u00e0 Panama.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sterling, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"De Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sterling, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/De-Bruyne-phat-bieu-ve-Sterling,-dong-doi-tai-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">De Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sterling v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Sterling th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 h\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Trong nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh lu\u00f4n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 l\u00f3ng ng\u00f3ng v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Sau khi Tam s\u01b0 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, Sterling c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>De Bruyne b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng hay h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 Sterling, De Bruyne \u0111\u1ee9ng ra b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n em t\u1ea1i Man City kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f3. &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00e0o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&rdquo;, De Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sterling.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y Sterling \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 t\u00f4i xem. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n, t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e1o ch\u00ed v\u00e0 gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh t\u00ecnh y\u00eau cho Sterling khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00ec \u0110T Anh ngay c\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-ly-do-khien-tam-su-khong-the-di-den-tran-dau-cuoi-cung-421-191024.html\">4 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Tam S\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/that-bai-cua-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-chi-la-bong-da-chua-the-tro-ve-466-191001.html\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/its-coming-home-niem-hy-vong-su-lo-bich-va-mong-ba-vuong-cua-tuyen-anh-421-190798.html\">&ldquo;It&rsquo;s Coming Home&rdquo; &ndash; Ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng, s\u1ef1 l\u1ed1 b\u1ecbch v\u00e0 m\u1ed9ng b\u00e1 v\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/that-bai-cua-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-chi-la-bong-da-chua-the-tro-ve-466-191001.html\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1221","checkdouble":"191106"},{"date":"15:48 13/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i tin \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/philipp-lahm-phat-bieu-ve-dt-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Conte ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Andreas Christensen</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Napoli l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t t\u1ee9 3 Serie A (sau Juventus v\u00e0 Roma), h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 38 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 58 tu\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/HLV-Maurizio-Sarri-toi-Chelsea-thay-Conte-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andreas Christensen nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri c\u00f3 t\u01b0 duy b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Pep Guardiola, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng ngay t\u1eeb b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ede Napoli, Kalidou Koulibaly l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 n\u00e0y. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a anh l\u00ean t\u1edbi 95% \u1edf Serie A 2017/18.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede Stamford Bridge, trung v\u1ec7 Andreas Christensen c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Conte s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChristensen c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 93,4%, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Koulibaly. N\u1ebfu HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Christensen s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Manchester City</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 35 v\u00e0 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-HLV-Sarri-dan-dat-Chelsea-thay-Conte-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri gi\u00fap Chelsea mua Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 b\u1edfi Jorginho \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Chelsea. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Anh \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 2 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 Napoli y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn The Blues theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; Jorginho c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ra m\u1eaft HLV Sarri. Theo ESPN, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft HLV Sarri v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u00e0 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Vi\u1ec7c Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn khi\u1ebfn Los Blancos d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri muon bien Hazard thanh trung tam trong loi choi cua Chelsea\" title=\"Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/ha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m nay, Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Hazard, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn NHM Chelsea lo l\u1eafng khi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Real c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. HLV Sarri d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea song mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 The Blues gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV 58 tu\u1ed5i d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea quanh Hazard, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 400.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i, t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a anh v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Blues \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Antonio Conte</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Conte l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho Chelsea trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7, theo \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u mang v\u1ec1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea thay conte sarri\" title=\"Chelsea thay conte sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/John-Terry-phat-bieu-ve-Antonio-Conte-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Conte b\u1ecb Chelsea th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 Conte \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 48 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu chung s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-conte-da-bi-chelsea-sa-thai-421-191062.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i</span>. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia th\u1ee9 9 m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Abramovich.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAn \u1ee7i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Conte l\u00e0 \u00f4ng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea. T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 c\u1ef1u HLV Juventus, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho c\u00e1c HLV.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ruben Loftus-Cheek</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n trong 2 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua s\u1eafm qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 HLV Sarri s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ruben Loftus-Cheek\" title=\"Ruben Loftus-Cheek\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/16/Thay-gi-sau-vu-tien-ve-Ross-Barkley-toi-Chelsea-hinh-anh-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ruben Loftus-Cheek \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Sarri s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y Ruben Loftus-Cheek l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Crystal Palace.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLoftus-Cheek th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu Sarri c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Alvaro Morata</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alvaro Morata \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Diego Costa \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/4-doi-bong-lon-san-sang-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-bom-xit-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata s\u1eafp b\u1eadt b\u00e3i kh\u1ecfi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i Morata ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. C\u1ef1u sao Real li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f2n tranh ch\u1ea5p r\u1ea5t k\u00e9m, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 Morata, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Dries Mertens c\u1ee7a Napoli ho\u1eb7c Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Conte t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb Morata c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh, song khi m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 48 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i c\u00f2n Sarri s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m, th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a Morata \u1edf Stamford Bridge ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n*Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1220","checkdouble":"191107"},{"date":"14:54 13/07","title":"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai G\u0110KT Gede s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/28/tuong-lai-gdkt-gede-sap-duoc-vff-dinh-doat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam VFF s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi G\u0110KT ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, Jurgen Gede theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m.</h2><h2>VFF gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/19/Tuong-lai-GDKT-Jurgen-Gede-sap-duoc-VFF-dinh-doat-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam VFF b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng Jurgen Gede l\u00e0m G\u0110KT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6/2016 theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m. B\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng th\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng trong c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb trong th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong su\u1ed1t hai n\u0103m qua, G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 &nbsp;VCK U20 World Cup, U15 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U15 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u \u00c1 qu\u00e2n VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a VFF. V\u00e0 sau 2 n\u0103m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, \u00f4ng Gede \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng khi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Gede v\u00e0 VFF s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n trong th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, sau khi \u00f4ng Gede tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 c\u00f9ng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, c\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c &ldquo;ch\u1ed1t&rdquo; h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi gi\u1eefa G\u0110KT Gede v\u00e0 VFF d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u00eam 2 n\u0103m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, G\u0110KT Gede s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch l\u1edbn trong 2 n\u0103m t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn ASIAD 2018, AFF Cup 2018 v\u00e0 VCK Asian Cup 2019.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1219","checkdouble":"191108"},{"date":"15:55 13/07","title":"N\u00f3ng: \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t \u2018Messi Th\u00e1i Lan\u2019","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/3/nong-doi-bong-nhat-ban-chinh-thuc-mua-dut-messi-thai-lan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecb thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c b\u1edfi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chanathip Songkrasin, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n Consadole Sapporo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Consadole Sapporo&nbsp;</span>ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t Chanathip Songkrasin</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chanathip Songkrasin t\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB Consadole Sapporo t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 7/2017 theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 1 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i.&nbsp;T\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &lsquo;Messi Jay&rsquo; \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t Chanathip Songkrasin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t Chanathip Songkrasin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/3/them-cau-thu-thai-lan-ghi-ban-o-giai-jleague-1-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Chanathip ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Consadole Sapporo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 1 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i J1 League, Chanathip \u0111\u00e3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0&nbsp;ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n trong 14 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho&nbsp;Consadole&nbsp;\u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa Consadole Sapporo v\u1edbi Consadole Sapporo, Chanathip ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap Consadole v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110N\u00c1 n\u00e0y, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Muangthong United. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 song ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Muangthong United s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 570 ngh\u00ecn USD (13,1 t\u1ec9&nbsp;\u0111\u1ed3ng) t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n Chanathip. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Consadole Sapporo mua \u0111\u1ee9t, Chanathip \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i J-League 1. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1218","checkdouble":"191109"}]}